name: Tezpunks
description:
Tezpunks

Year AD 7702, a group of deadly punks with superpowers are assigned a mysterious mission.  
Objectives of the mission will be communicated to them from the command center.For now,the only objective communicated to the punks is to time travel to 2021. 

ID #017
Non Binary

Name         : Bohzij 
Strength     : 93/100
Intelligence : 88/100

Bohzij was a pirate who lived in the times of Ramses, the 2nd. His ship and the whole crew inside was set to fire by pharaoh’s army while they tried to attack a ship laden with precious jewels and gold. Bohzij and his crew were given lives back by the Gurhav twins.
